<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='628812' id='t-628812'>in the various videos
that you've seen here.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='630889' id='t-630889'>We want to try to simulate
the experience for the world</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='633489' id='t-633489'>that we're actually seeing
through the glasses,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='635706' id='t-635706'>and not cut any corners.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
10:47
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='636881' id='t-636881'>CA: Thank you so much for showing us that.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
10:49
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='638929' id='t-638929'>MG: Thanks so much, I appreciate that.</span>
</span>
</p>
